text: Edmund Pueschel (January 31, 1883 - August 6, 1959) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1959 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kansas City, Missouri
